<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 14:06:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列在最后一刻将 800 万美元用于犹太人身份纳入国家预算</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-slips-8-million-for-jewish-identity-at-last-minute-into-state-budget/0000018e-281e-d1b8-a5de-e9de10d30000</link><description>诺姆党请求议会批准追加资金，该资金将用于“促进团结和相互责任，加强对社会和国家的志愿服务精神”以及有关犹太身份问题的“公共外交和广告”等举措</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 12:04:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-slips-8-million-for-jewish-identity-at-last-minute-into-state-budget/0000018e-281e-d1b8-a5de-e9de10d30000</guid></item><item><title>在所有会议之母上，以色列妇女希望在开创性反战运动的成功基础上再接再厉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/at-mother-of-all-conferences-israeli-women-look-to-build-on-success-of-anti-war-movement/0000018e-27fa-d1b8-a5de-e7fe07900000</link><description>上周在耶路撒冷举行的一次会议探讨了母性的概念及其在政治组织和激进主义中的作用，团结是当前各种运动（从母亲支持生命到母亲反对暴力）之间的关键目标</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 11:38:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/at-mother-of-all-conferences-israeli-women-look-to-build-on-success-of-anti-war-movement/0000018e-27fa-d1b8-a5de-e7fe07900000</guid></item><item><title>斋月祈祷将于周日在耶路撒冷开始，使加沙战争的紧张局势达到潜在的临界点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/ramadan-set-to-begin-in-jerusalem-sunday-bringing-tensions-over-gaza-war-to-peak/0000018e-279b-d152-ad8e-2ffbf5610000</link><description>在政府决定在哈马斯战争期间不再实施新的入境限制后，数千名穆斯林信徒抵达阿克萨/圣殿山大院将使以色列的政策面临考验。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 10:04:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/ramadan-set-to-begin-in-jerusalem-sunday-bringing-tensions-over-gaza-war-to-peak/0000018e-279b-d152-ad8e-2ffbf5610000</guid></item><item><title>以色列首席塞法迪拉比：如果他们强迫我们参军，我们都会离开这个国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/chief-sephardic-rabbi-if-they-force-us-to-go-to-the-army-well-leave-israel/0000018e-2768-d152-ad8e-2fe86ad80000</link><description>首席拉比发表上述言论之际，该州向高等法院解释为什么不征召极端正统派男子入伍——尽管豁免他们服役的法律已经到期</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 09:27:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/chief-sephardic-rabbi-if-they-force-us-to-go-to-the-army-well-leave-israel/0000018e-2768-d152-ad8e-2fe86ad80000</guid></item><item><title>考古学家在耶路撒冷附近发现迦南“旭日神庙”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-03-10/ty-article/archaeologists-discover-canaanite-temple-of-the-rising-sun-in-central-israel/0000018e-26fe-d7d3-abce-66ffa0260000</link><description>这座建于 3,300 年前的纪念性建筑在阿西卡山顶的晨光下闪闪发光，显示出与古埃及的密切文化联系</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 06:44:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-03-10/ty-article/archaeologists-discover-canaanite-temple-of-the-rising-sun-in-central-israel/0000018e-26fe-d7d3-abce-66ffa0260000</guid></item><item><title>数十枚火箭弹向以色列北部发射； 7名阿拉伯裔以色列人因恐怖罪名被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article-live/biden-there-is-a-red-line-cannot-have-30-000-more-palestinians-dead/0000018e-2684-d152-ad8e-2fece7420000</link><description>美国总统拜登在 MSNBC 采访中警告称，“不会再有 30,000 名巴勒斯坦人死亡” ■ 美国陆军派遣船只前往加沙，运送临时援助港口的物资 ■ 据报道，以色列发动的袭击在黎巴嫩造成 5 人死亡、9 人受伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 04:36:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article-live/biden-there-is-a-red-line-cannot-have-30-000-more-palestinians-dead/0000018e-2684-d152-ad8e-2fece7420000</guid></item><item><title>在没有人质协议的情况下，美国限制以色列在加沙的行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/in-absence-of-hostage-deal-u-s-reining-in-israels-actions-in-gaza/0000018e-24e6-dc52-abff-65e6a3230000</link><description>在援助车队事件造成人员伤亡以及以色列政府对阻止援助进入加沙的示威活动不采取行动之后，美国修建海港的计划反映了华盛顿基调的转变。哈马斯无需做出重大让步就能获益，其达成协议的动力可能会下降</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 04:14:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/in-absence-of-hostage-deal-u-s-reining-in-israels-actions-in-gaza/0000018e-24e6-dc52-abff-65e6a3230000</guid></item><item><title>拜登：拉法行动“是一条红线”，内塔尼亚胡“对以色列的伤害大于帮助”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/biden-warns-netanyahu-hurting-israel-more-than-helping-says-he-wants-to-address-knesset/0000018e-25b7-d7d3-abce-65bfc0d40000</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登在发表国情咨文演讲 48 小时后接受 MSNBC 采访时表示，“追击哈马斯不会导致 3 万名巴勒斯坦人死亡，还有其他方法”</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 00:35:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/biden-warns-netanyahu-hurting-israel-more-than-helping-says-he-wants-to-address-knesset/0000018e-25b7-d7d3-abce-65bfc0d40000</guid></item><item><title>调查发现 18 岁嫌疑人背部中枪，与警方的说法相矛盾</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/investigation-finds-18-year-old-suspect-shot-from-the-back-contradicting-polices-version/0000018e-2512-d7d3-abce-65bbd99a0000</link><description>警方调查发现，一名二月份被杀的犯罪嫌疑人背部被连中三枪，这与枪手声称嫌疑人试图用刀袭击他的说法相矛盾，这一说法最初得到了警方的认可</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 23:12:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/investigation-finds-18-year-old-suspect-shot-from-the-back-contradicting-polices-version/0000018e-2512-d7d3-abce-65bbd99a0000</guid></item><item><title>数千以色列人抗议政府，警察在特拉维夫使用高压水枪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-israelis-protest-govt-police-use-water-cannons-in-tel-aviv/0000018e-24d8-dc52-abff-65da956f0000</link><description>16人在以色列各地举行的反对本杰明·内塔尼亚胡政府的示威活动中被捕，这些示威活动包括海法、贝尔谢巴、凯撒利亚和特拉维夫，抗议者暂时封锁了特拉维夫的阿亚隆高速公路</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 20:42:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-israelis-protest-govt-police-use-water-cannons-in-tel-aviv/0000018e-24d8-dc52-abff-65da956f0000</guid></item><item><title>数千人在庆祝国际妇女节时呼吁达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/.premium/thousands-call-for-a-hostage-deal-while-marking-international-womens-day/0000018e-248d-dbcf-abee-3dddf72e0000</link><description>在特拉维夫人质广场举行的集会上，纪念战争结束 155 天和国际妇女节，希伯来语和阿拉伯语视频强调，“社会无法开始复苏，仍有 134 名男女仍被哈马斯囚禁”</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 19:57:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/.premium/thousands-call-for-a-hostage-deal-while-marking-international-womens-day/0000018e-248d-dbcf-abee-3dddf72e0000</guid></item><item><title>一天之内，以色列各地发生四起枪击事件，造成五人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/.premium/two-arab-israelis-shot-dead-in-southern-israel-in-third-shooting-incident-in-one-day/0000018e-24b1-dc52-abff-65b37d020000</link><description>一名男子坐在车里被杀，另外两人在以色列南部城市阿拉德附近的一个加油站被枪杀，一名 33 岁男子在德鲁兹城镇马加尔被枪杀，一名五个孩子的母亲被枪杀海法一家具乐部外</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 19:52:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/.premium/two-arab-israelis-shot-dead-in-southern-israel-in-third-shooting-incident-in-one-day/0000018e-24b1-dc52-abff-65b37d020000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队命名周五在加沙战斗中丧生的预备役人员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/israeli-army-names-reservist-killed-in-gaza-combat-on-friday/0000018e-247b-dbf3-a1bf-a7ff936e0000</link><description>阿米沙尔·本·大卫 (Amishar Ben David) 少校，43 岁，来自伊莱定居点，曾担任突击队指挥官，在与恐怖分子的战斗中身亡。他是一名高中教师和红大卫盾会志愿者，身后留下了妻子和五个孩子</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 18:55:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/israeli-army-names-reservist-killed-in-gaza-combat-on-friday/0000018e-247b-dbf3-a1bf-a7ff936e0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 155 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-155/0000018e-2452-d7d3-abce-64fbfecc0000</link><description>中央司令部否认美国空投杀害巴勒斯坦平民 ■ 哈马斯敦促巴勒斯坦人在斋月期间游行到圣殿山/阿克萨清真寺 ■ 近东救济工程处指责以色列强迫机构工作人员错误地承认哈马斯的联系 ■ 加拿大、瑞典恢复对近东救济工程处的资助 ■ 拜登：“看起来强硬” &amp;#39; 以便在斋月之前实现停火 ■ 这是战争开始 155 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 18:04:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-155/0000018e-2452-d7d3-abce-64fbfecc0000</guid></item><item><title>近东救济工程处指责以色列强迫机构工作人员错误地承认与哈马斯有联系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/unrwa-accuses-israel-of-forcing-agency-staff-to-falsely-admit-hamas-links/0000018e-2083-dbcf-abee-39db85560000</link><description>联合国机构的一份报告详细介绍了对家庭成员的严重殴打、水刑和伤害威胁的指控</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 15:21:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/unrwa-accuses-israel-of-forcing-agency-staff-to-falsely-admit-hamas-links/0000018e-2083-dbcf-abee-39db85560000</guid></item><item><title>由于亲巴勒斯坦抗议的威胁，第三届 Matisyahu 音乐会被取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-03-09/ty-article/third-matisyahu-concert-canceled-amid-threat-of-pro-palestinian-protests/0000018e-2397-dbcf-abee-3bdf4a9f0000</link><description>继亚利桑那州和新墨西哥州取消了这位犹太雷鬼歌手的音乐会后，芝加哥的一个场馆也取消了音乐会。场馆在成为抗议者的目标后提到了安全问题，抗议者声称为以色列士兵和亲以色列团体表演应该取消马蒂亚胡的表演资格</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 15:07:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-03-09/ty-article/third-matisyahu-concert-canceled-amid-threat-of-pro-palestinian-protests/0000018e-2397-dbcf-abee-3bdf4a9f0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登：有红线，不能再让3万巴勒斯坦人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article-live/biden-doubts-gaza-cease-fire-by-ramadan-fears-escalating-violence-in-jerusalem/0000018e-2103-d7d3-abce-61ab371d0000</link><description>以色列各地爆发要求释放人质的反政府抗议活动 ■ 以色列国防军北方司令部司令：我们一直在为黎巴嫩的进攻做准备 近东救济工程处 ■ 机构负责人表示，“面临死亡风险” ■ 中央司令部否认美国空投导致加沙死亡周五平民 美国副总统哈里斯向哥伦比亚广播公司新闻表示：区分以色列政府和以色列人民很重要</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 02:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article-live/biden-doubts-gaza-cease-fire-by-ramadan-fears-escalating-violence-in-jerusalem/0000018e-2103-d7d3-abce-61ab371d0000</guid></item><item><title>七名以色列士兵在约旦河西岸被爆炸装置炸伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/.premium/seven-israeli-soldiers-wounded-by-explosive-devise-in-west-bank/0000018e-200f-df70-a1bf-67df5e910000</link><description>当士兵们追击巴勒斯坦人时，爆炸物被引爆，巴勒斯坦人向霍姆什前哨附近的以色列国防军哨所开枪。三人受中度伤。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 22:27:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/.premium/seven-israeli-soldiers-wounded-by-explosive-devise-in-west-bank/0000018e-200f-df70-a1bf-67df5e910000</guid></item><item><title>非政府组织联盟表示，以色列拒绝续签约旦河西岸和加沙的援助人员签证，在关键时刻损害了援助工作</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/ngos-israel-pausing-aid-worker-visas-in-west-bank-gaza-harms-humanitarian-efforts/0000018e-1fb4-d7d3-abce-7fbdf55b0000</link><description>这个名为国际开发机构协会（AIDA）的联盟表示，其成员发挥了关键作用，并且在以色列与哈马斯加沙战争进行五个多月后迫切需要该联盟。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 20:47:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/ngos-israel-pausing-aid-worker-visas-in-west-bank-gaza-harms-humanitarian-efforts/0000018e-1fb4-d7d3-abce-7fbdf55b0000</guid></item><item><title>加拿大表示将恢复向近东救济工程处提供资金，并指出该机构在加沙的“重要作用”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/canada-says-it-will-resume-unrwa-funding-cites-its-vital-role-in-gaza/0000018e-1fb7-df70-a1bf-7fff5e550000</link><description>在以色列指控近东救济工程处的 12 名工作人员参与了哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击后，包括美国和英国在内的 16 个捐助者暂停了对近东救济工程处的资助</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 20:29:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/canada-says-it-will-resume-unrwa-funding-cites-its-vital-role-in-gaza/0000018e-1fb7-df70-a1bf-7fff5e550000</guid></item></channel></rss>